r allies or enemies who help or hinder their journey.\",\"status\":\"in progress\"},{\"id\":\"SQ003\",\"title\":\"The Lost Ward Circle\",\"description\":\"An ancient protective ward circle in the forest has failed. Restoring it could weaken the keep's influence and protect the village from spectral incursions.\",\"status\":\"not started\"},{\"id\":\"SQ004\",\"title\":\"The Keeper's Warning\",\"description\":\"A mysterious hermit known as the Keeper dwells near the forest edge. They possess knowledge about the keep's curse but require assistance or convincing to share it.\",\"status\":\"not started\"}]}\n"
