    "content": "{\n  \"narration\": \"The Wyrd Lantern Inn welcomes you with a comforting warmth and the subtle aroma of roasting meat and fresh bread. Lanterns flicker along the rafters, casting golden light across the worn timber beams. Villagers cluster around tables, their voices low but friendly, while Cira the innkeeper offers you a nod and a steaming mug of herbal tea.\\n\\nYou settle into a corner seat, letting the gentle bustle and familiar sounds ease your nerves. The exhaustion of your earlier ordeals presses upon you, and as you finish your meal, you feel the tension ebbing away. Cira checks in on you from time to time, her smile reassuring. \\\"You rest as long as you need, love. The shadows won't find you here.\\\"\\n\\nGradually, your aches fade and your spirit finds respite. The hours pass quietly, the sounds of laughter and clattering mugs lulling you into a peaceful rest. You sense that, for now, you are safe.\",\n  \"actions\": [\n    {\n      \"action\": \"updateTime\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"timeEstimate\": 60\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"action\": \"updatePlayerInfo\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"changes\": \"Norn takes a short rest at the inn, spending an hour to recover. Norn may roll Hit Dice to regain hit points and is refreshed for the next leg of the journey.\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"
