    "content": "{\n  \"narration\": \"You bid Cira farewell, her warm smile fading into concern as she watches you shoulder your pack and step out into the village streets. The air outside carries a faint chill, and the sun hangs low in the spring sky. As you make your way through Harrow's Hollow, villagers nod in greeting, some offering quiet words of encouragement or hope.\\n\\nYour boots carry you past the general store and along the familiar path to the East Gate and Guardhouse. The guards there recognize you, their wary expressions softening. One gives you a respectful nod as you approach the gate leading out toward the Witchlight Trail.\\n\\nA hush falls as you step beyond the village's safe embrace, the sounds of daily life replaced by the distant caw of a raven and the whisper of wind through budding trees. The gate swings closed behind you, marking the boundary between the everyday and the unknown.\\n\\nYou are now at the East Gate and Guardhouse, poised to continue onward to the Witchlight Trailhead or prepare as you see fit.\",\n  \"actions\": [\n    {\n      \"action\": \"transitionLocation\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"newLocation\": \"East Gate and Guardhouse\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"action\": \"updateTime\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"timeEstimate\": 5\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"
